        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " function is a scalar function in Microsoft SQL Server designed to calculate and apply a monthly percentage to electric billing data that spans across different billing periods. This function is typically used in scenarios where electric consumption needs to be prorated or adjusted based on specific monthly percentages, which may be necessary for accurate billing or reporting."
